ManySmallTweaks allows Bukkit admins to enable several different tweaks on a per-world basis. 
The tweaks currently include: FloatingLadders, FloatingRails, FloatingHatch, ButtonsOnMoreBlocks, 
RedstoneIgnitesNetherrack, PercentColorSheep, PercentSaddledPigs, KeepSaddleOnPigDeath, 
InfiniteCauldrons, ProjectileTriggers, PigsReproduceQuick, RedstoneIgnitesPumpkins,
FloatingPaintings